Intro Area
==========

The shores give way to cliffs. The pathway forward is through twisty winding paths through wooded areas buffered by steep cliffs. Progress requires retrieving three crystal shards, each guarded by a Vulfebeast. The three shards can be assembled inside a stone obelisk which creates a bridge leading to a town.
